name: SQL Queries Priority Docs
jql: project = DOC AND issuetype in (Docs) AND status not in (Done, Duplicate, Cancelled) AND priority in (Highest, High) AND Product Area[Dropdown]" = "Data Int - SQL Queries" ORDER BY status DESC

name: SQL Schema & Migrations Priority Docs
jql: project = DOC AND issuetype in (Docs, Epic) AND status in (Backlog, In Progress"
column11: High) AND "Product Area[Select List (cascading)]" in ("SQL Schema & Migrations") ORDER BY status DESC

name: SQL Session Priority Docs
jql: project = DOC AND issuetype in (Docs, Epic) AND status in (Backlog, In Progress"
column11: High) AND "Product Area[Dropdown]" = "Data Int - SQL Sessions" ORDER BY status DESC

name: SREOPS (highest priority)
jql: project = SRE Operations" and ("Engineering Team[Dropdown]" = SRE or "Engineering Team[Dropdown]" is EMPTY)  and statusCategory != Done and priority = Highest order by duedate ASC"

name: High Priority Docs
jql: project = Documentation and priority in (Highest, High) order by created DESC

name: Priority = Highest, High Docs
jql: project = DOC AND issuetype in (Docs, Epic) AND status in (Backlog, In Progress"
column11: High) AND "Product Area[Select List (cascading)]" in cascadeOption(10063

name: Migrations Priority Docs
jql: project = DOC AND issuetype in (Docs) AND status not in (Done, Duplicate, Cancelled) AND priority in (Highest, High) AND Product Area[Dropdown]" = "ADE - Migrations" ORDER BY status DESC

name: Customer Success - High and Critical Priority
jql: project = CS AND priority in (Highest, High) order by created DESC
